title: AFC/NFC predictions; Cowboys, Bucs X Factors; Tony Gonzalez
itunes:title: AFC/NFC predictions; Cowboys, Bucs X Factors; Tony Gonzalez
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Michael Robinson Peter Schrager and Kyle Brandt share their NFC and AFC playoff predictions; they dive into potential x-factors in the Dallas Cowboys vs. Tampa Bay Buccaneers game; Tom Pelissero shares details on the Baltimore Ravens running backs; and Tony Gonzalez joins to share his thoughts on Kyle Pitts, Julio Jones and the emotions you have when you face your former team!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
